Class JdbcSimpleAttributeLoaderListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.tsgrp.migration.event.AbstractListener

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    SourceEndExportNodeEventListener

    public class JdbcSimpleAttributeLoaderListener
extends AbstractListener
implements SourceEndExportNodeEventListener
    Execute a SQL query (using a JDBC connection) and place resulting values into the current node, using the column names as the attribute names.
